trans-unit.source: Represents a variable within a symbol store.
trans-unit.target: 表示符号存储区内的变量。

trans-unit.source: The ISymbolVariable interface can be a parameter, a local variable, or a field.
trans-unit.target: 该 ISymbolVariable 界面可以是参数、 本地变量或字段。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This interface is the managed counterpart of the `ISymUnmanagedVariable` interface, which is one of the unmanaged symbol store interfaces that provide an alternate way to read and write debug symbol information.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE]&1;> 此接口是托管的副本的`ISymUnmanagedVariable`接口，该提供另一种方法来读取和写入调试符号信息的非托管的符号存储区接口之一。

trans-unit.source: Gets the first address of a variable.
trans-unit.target: 获取变量的第一个地址。

trans-unit.target: 有关使用此属性的详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymAddressKind>枚举。</xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymAddressKind>
